Link of Question :- https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/281/A

Java Code :-

import java.util.*;  //import the java.util library

public class CF172_A {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner cs=new Scanner(System.in);
        String st=cs.next();
        cs.close();
        System.out.print(st.substring(0,1).toUpperCase()+st.substring(1));
    }
}
